AUDIO: 'I\'ve tested a ton of wireless microphones over the years, and each time I test Saramonic, their microphones usually have the best range, and every single time they have had the best audio quality. Today, we\'re checking out their newest microphone. This is the AirSE. It'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
